<i>Posted by Barmoz on 11-19-2002 09:41 PM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>For what it's worth, and it may be completely unrelated to the problems you're having, but rumor has it they broke serverfiltering recently, so if it's a problem that occurs more when you're around a lot of people rather than just a gradual buildup over time of lag, that may be part of it.</p>

